      <title>
         <ph props="autonumber">237.170-1</ph> Scope.</title>
      <conbody>
         <p>This section—</p>
         <p outputclass="List1">(a)  Implements 10 U.S.C. 2330; and</p>
         <p outputclass="List1">(b)  Applies to services acquired for DoD, regardless of whether the services are acquired through—</p>
         <p outputclass="List2">(1)  A DoD contract or task order; or</p>
         <p outputclass="List2">(2)  A contract or task order awarded by an agency other than DoD.</p>
      </conbody>
